Deployment Instructions
Save the code as john_ko_radar.html.
Host it on any web server (e.g., GitHub Pages, Netlify, or a local server like XAMPP).
Open the file in a browser to view John Ko's radar chart.
Features
Displays a single radar chart for John Ko with his scores.
Uses Chart.js for a clean, responsive visualization.
Simple, lightweight, and production-ready with no external dependencies beyond the Chart.js CDN.
No user input required; data is hardcoded for reliability.
Responsive design works on desktop and mobile devices.
